com.adobe.creativesdk.behance

Class AdobeBehanceUpdateProfileOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.adobe.creativesdk.behance.AdobeBehanceUpdateProfileOptions

  • public class AdobeBehanceUpdateProfileOptions
extends java.lang.Object
    AdobeBehanceUpdateProfileOptions represents the options for the updating Behance user profile. This class acts as an interface to get/set the fields (mentioned below) associated with the user profile.
    • First Name - first name of the user.
    • Last Name - last name of the user.
    • Occupation - occupation of the user.
    • Company - company with which the user is associated with.
    • Website - personal blog/website of the user.
    • Country - the country where the user resides.
    • State - the state in which the user resides.
    • City - the city in which the user resides.
    • Image - profile image of the user.
